how can you get paint out of the carpet i was painting my room using disney behr paint now i used tarp but there are still a few small drops splotches here and there soap and water isn't able to remove it how do i get it out help use scissors and very lighty cut away the spots hardware stores have a specialty tool for carpetlayers that are like scissors but are designed to cut parallel with the carpet if you use ordinary scissors be sure to keep the scissors as parallel to the carpet as possible if you angle the scissors too much while cutting you might gouge too deep Drill bit Rock, Paper, Scissors Carpet Manicure Bong W. Daniel Hillis Woodturning Floppy disk Professional wrestling holds Glossary of American football Scissors Woodworking Basement Lawn mower Vacuum cleaner Wood carving Wound PlayStation 3 Glossary of firefighting equipment Anchor Tag Plane (tool) Cut and paste Fenway Park Gouge Nail (anatomy) Supercomputer Textile manufacturing Dial M for Murder Chisel Table saw Textile manufacturing terminology Railroad switch Vickers Valiant Sharpening stone Knife Roomba Upholstery Tattoo CPU cache Magical objects in Harry Potter Drawing Screw Firefighter CPU design Professional wrestling attacks Professional wrestling throws Worms weapons and tools Breaststroke Glossary of wildland fire terms Xanadu House Fire fighting Glasses Fabrication (metal) Stamp collecting RISC Dollar store Sundial Surrealist techniques N-Gage Glass Department store Die (manufacturing) Running with Scissors (film) Sprite (computer graphics) Wallpaper group Digital circuit Wrench Magnetic resonance imaging Engraving Sears Holdings Corporation Pliers Indecent pseudo-photograph of a child "Weird Al" Yankovic View camera Spirit rover Screenshot Roger Federer Microphone Japanese tea ceremony Diamond cut Casting Circuit design Machinima Disney's California Adventure Sound effect Animal Crossing Einstein-Cartan theory Central processing unit Leaf 2D computer graphics Liquid crystal Adventureland 